videos.description: Jack White finds an opening and drives down the lane before finishing at the rim with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: White throws it down for Duke slam

videos.description: Elijah Thomas sends a nice bounce pass to Aamir Simms who hammers it home and gets fouled for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Clemson's Simms punishes rim on and-1

videos.description: Trevon Duval capitalizes on a poor pass by Clemson, then zooms to the other end and hammers it home late in the first half.
videos.headline: Clemson turnover creates wide-open Duke hoop

videos.description: Marcquise Reed takes advantage of David Skara's steal to knock down a wide-open 3-pointer for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Clemson's Reed splashes home 3-pointer after steal

videos.description: Trevon Duval drives to the basket with his right and switches to his left before getting a crafty layup to fall for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke's Duval attacks the rack

videos.description: Marcquise Reed drives through the lane and gets a layup to fall despite the contact.
videos.headline: Clemson's Reed drops in clutch and-1 layup

videos.description: Gabe DeVoe knocks down his first 3-pointer of the game to bring Clemson within 2 points of Duke late in the second half.
videos.headline: Clemson's DeVoe excites crowd with huge 3-pointer

videos.description: Wendell Carter Jr. hits his defender with a turnaround jumper in the paint to seal it for the Blue Devils.
videos.headline: Duke's Carter dominates the paint in crunch time

videos.description: Duke finishes the game on a 9-0 run to defeat Clemson 66-57.
videos.headline: Duke holds off Clemson
